<section sectnbr = "4A">
<servcat sctnbr = "04" scnbr = "01">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENAP70B4106018" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Brake Master Cylinder Reservoir Removal and Installation
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B4106015">Brake Master Cylinder Components</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Do not allow brake fluid to get on painted surfaces. Painted surfaces will be damaged by brake fluid. If any fluid is spilled, flush it with water immediately.
</ptxt>
</attention2>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B4106018001">
<title>
Removal
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Clean outside surface of reservoir.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove brake master cylinder together with reservoir from brake booster.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove spring pin (1) by using special tool.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L4A006">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-44310">
09916–44310
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A410013.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.801mm" ver = "01" gw = "138" gh = "127"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove reservoir (1) and grommets (2).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A410014.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "70.866mm" ver = "01" gw = "152" gh = "184"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B4106018002">
<title>
Installation
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
When using new grommets, lubricate them with the same brake fluid as the one to fill reservoir before fitting grommets into master cylinder.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install reservoir to brake master cylinder.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install spring pin (2) by using special tool, until both of its ends at the right and left of reservoir (1) becomes the same length.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L4A007">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-44310">
09916–44310
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I8C50A410025.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "44.650mm" ver = "01" gw = "193" gh = "110"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install brake master cylinder with reservoir to brake booster.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
